OL,3,CWhere are the wildfires and how
OL,4,Cdangerous are they?
OL,6,FWildfires have been reported across
OL,7,Flarge parts of England in the last 48
OL,8,Fhours.
OL,10,FWith a third heatwave in as many
OL,11,Fmonths ` and our current one set to
OL,12,Flast another week ` the conditions are
OL,13,Fsuch that more could follow.
OL,15,FAfter eight days of hot, strong
OL,16,Fsunshine and temperatures consistently
OL,17,F30C or more across huge swathes of the
OL,18,FUK, the ground is tinder dry ` and it
OL,19,Fdoesn't take much for an existing fire
OL,20,Fto spread.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
