OL,3,CWhere are the wildfires and how
OL,4,Cdangerous are they?
OL,6,FMany areas of England and Wales have
OL,7,Fnot seen any rain at all this month,
OL,8,Fwith the last notable rainfall and
OL,9,Fthundery downpours three weeks ago.
OL,11,FOver the weekend, blustery winds
OL,12,Fpicked up in places, exacerbating the
OL,13,Frisk of fires moving at an accelerated
OL,14,Fpace in the more vulnerable locations.
OL,16,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,17,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,18,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,19,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,21,FHow do I know if my area is at risk?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
