OL,3,CWhere are the wildfires and how
OL,4,Cdangerous are they?
OL,6,FThe following areas feature patches
OL,7,Fwith "exceptional risk" of wildfires
OL,8,Fat the time of writing:
OL,10,FHuge stretches of England have "very
OL,11,Fhigh" risk warnings and you can find
OL,12,Fdetails for your area on the Fire
OL,13,FSeverity Index website.
OL,15,FWhat can you do about wildfires?
OL,17,FWhen wildfire conditions are elevated,
OL,18,Fany fire that takes hold can be more
OL,19,Fdifficult to control and extinguish,
OL,20,Fparticularly where blustery winds
OL,21,Fallow it to spread more easily.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
