OL,3,CWhere are the wildfires and how
OL,4,Cdangerous are they?
OL,6,FIn the UK, the majority of wildfires
OL,7,Fare started by human activity, such as
OL,8,Fdiscarded cigarettes, campfires or
OL,9,Funattended barbecues.
OL,11,FThe British Red Cross provides the
OL,12,Ffollowing advice to help prevent
OL,13,Fwildfires:
OL,15,FWith no notable rain in the forecast,
OL,16,Fthe risk in many areas remains high.
OL,18,FHow can wildfires affect me?
OL,20,FWildfires can have impacts far beyond
OL,21,Fthe area where the flames are burning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
