OL,3,CWhere are the wildfires and how
OL,4,Cdangerous are they?
OL,6,FSmoke can travel many miles, reducing
OL,7,Fvisibility on roads and affecting air
OL,8,Fquality.
OL,10,FThis can lead to travel disruption,
OL,11,Fwith roads sometimes closed by
OL,12,Femergency services to protect the
OL,13,Fpublic and allow firefighters and
OL,14,Fother responders to work safely.
OL,16,FFor communities nearby, wildfires can
OL,17,Fmean changes to daily routines, from
OL,18,Favoiding affected areas to following
OL,19,Fadvice on air quality and travel.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
